{
  "stem": "11882.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When they went into Nuremberg, we had guards outside our doors every night, burning their fires in the cold winter air, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were always under protection and never mingled in any way with the so-called natives, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The indigenous, we called them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a big barrier there because they feared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They feared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were still rumors that Hitler still was alive and that the werewolves were there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some sort of magic German people that would some-- take over again sometime, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, a few days after we started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were a group of eight or nine people that got onto our airplane with a lot of pre-training; a day or two how to rescue ourselves at sea.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was scared to death to fly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I told Colonel Dostert, and he said, it's nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, I've flown that ocean 23 times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't think about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Colonel Dostert, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was scared to death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I thought, well, I really should do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I took out $50,000 of life insurance before I got in the airplane.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I thought, well that will do some good, anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as I came this time, I asked-- I guess it's true.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't believe you can take out life insurance anymore when you go take a sea voyage.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They don't want you to bomb the plane, I guess, you know, and get some cash out of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But at any rate, we arrived in Paris.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "First we stopped in Bermuda.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And everywhere we went, the plane was something wrong with it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had to spend 10 hours in bed there, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then we went on to the Azores.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Things were not so up to date as they are today.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
